Title: ã€Announcementã€‘BitMart Trading Platform is Comingï¼
Body: Dear BitMart User,  Thanks for being a valued user.  First of all, please be responsible for your words.  BitMart is a professional digital assets exchange registered as an MSB under FinCEN. We NEVER require KYC before deposit. However, we do require KYC when users need to withdraw and we NEVER failed users' KYC for irrational reasons. Our customer services have been distributing much of their time and efforts to assist users to complete their KYC, resubmit their KYC if they failed for the first time or for several times. We passed every user who submits their legal ID and personal information followed our requirements. We have more than 800,000 users globally and we never hear such kind of news complaining about our KYC process!! The KYC is for the safety of every users' assets and we clearly notify users in our user's policy.  We appreciate you being a BitMart user and please let us know if you have any misunderstanding about our KYC. Thanks!

Body: ğŸ‰BitMart lists Gemini dollar (GUSD)!  ğŸ‰BitMart lists Gemini dollar (GUSD)! GUSD/USDT trading pair is available now. More trading pairs will be announced soon. Please note the deposit and trading features are available now and the available date for withdrawal function will be announced later.  The Gemini dollar is a cryptographic token that is issued by a New York trust company, strictly pegged 1:1 to the U.S. dollar, and built on the Ethereum network according to the ERC20 standard for tokens. The Gemini dollar is a stable value coin that combines the creditworthiness and price stability of the U.S. dollar with the technological advantages of a cryptocurrency and the oversight of U.S. regulators. As an ERC20 compliant token, the Gemini dollar can be transferred on the Ethereum network. Gemini dollars are created at the time of withdrawal from the Gemini platform and redeemed or â€œdestroyedâ€ at the time of deposit into the Gemini platform.  Details: https://support.bitmart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360011132213-BitMart-Lists-Gemini-Dollar-GUSD-  https://i.imgur.com/h8Qujdm.png

Body: BitMart Lists Incodium (INCO)  BitMart lists Incodium (INCO). INCO/BTC and INCO/ETH trading pairs are now available. Start depositing and trading today at www.bitmart.com!!! Don't forget to participate in our Refer-A-Friend Program and Registration and Referral Sign-Up Bonus!  Check our website for more information: https://support.bitmart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360008938834-BitMart-Lists-Incodium-INCO-  The mission of Incodium is to provide a rational way for investors to cope with the treat of exchange hacking by providing a â€œsmart compensation protectionâ€ service for eligible victims of the exchange hacking. Build on the Ethereum platform, Incodium presents a solution that is simple, actionable and transparent. Investors are eligible to receive Incodium coin into their Incodium Mobile Wallet as a compensation for exchange hacking damage incurred on an exchange where Incodium coin is listed, with respect to all types of coins lost during the exchange hacking incident. We describe this as â€œsmart compensation protectionâ€ service. These selfsame investors are eligible for this compensation once they store Incodium coin in the incodium Mobile Wallet. The compensation amount received is based on a simple set of rules written in a smart contract as well as the current value of Incodium coin held in the Incodium Mobile Wallet at the time of the hacking incident. Eligible victims will receive the lowest of the three values as compensation in the form of Incodium coin: 30 times the amount of Incodium coins held in the Incodium Mobile Wallet; the amount for actual damages; or 10,000 USD  For more information about INCO, please click here.  https://i.imgur.com/NO2TDiq.jpg

Author: BitMartExchange
Title: ã€Announcementã€‘BitMart Trading Platform is Comingï¼
Body: For the purposes of BMX. Firstly, when users conduct transactions on BitMart, they will get a discount on the transaction fee if they have BMX, no matter what tokens they trade. Based on the current market value, the system will convert the amount to be paid into the equivalent amount of BMX and then the payment will be made with BMX. Besides, we have the Repurchase Mechanism, which means the BitMart team will take out 20% of the income earned by trading fees on the platform every month to repurchase BMX. The repurchased BMX will be destroyed completely and repurchase records will be released immediately. Users can check related information via the blockchain browser so that openness and transparency are guaranteed. The repurchase mechanism will continue to work until 500 million BMX are destroyed.

The NASDAQ Tower is considered the most visible LED video display in Times Square and is one of the most valuable advertising spaces in the world. It is used to celebrate corporate milestones. Advertising BitMart on the display tower signifies that digital asset trading platforms have entered into the mainstream.  BitMart launched its platform in March 2018. The platform now has 18 trading pairs available and is continuing to list new coins every week. With more than 400,000 users from over 160 countries, BitMart has built a team of top industry professionals from all over the world including the United States, Russia, India, Singapore, Japan and Hong Kong.  It goes a long way to build trust in the crypto market, so BitMart has a strong team of developers to ensure the security of usersâ€™ assets and transactions. In addition to purchasing space in Times Square, BitMartâ€™s Marketing team has built awareness through social and native advertising, engaged in large-scale blockchain events, forums, and international conferences in the fintech and blockchain industry. They also have a strong Legal Compliance team that provides a full range legal consultation and that helps to create competitive strategies within the current legal framework of the world.  https://i.imgur.com/H0HfwAl.png  Vision of the Future: A Whole-network Trading Platform  BitMart currently implements a 0% trading fee which is very rare compared to other participants in the market. BitMart recently launched a Millions of Cryptocandy Airdrop as well where registered users can claim free BTC, ETH, EOS, VEN, ABT, XLM, MOBI, BMX and many more tokens listed on BitMart daily by visiting https://www.bitmart.com/candy.html.  In an effort to reward users even further, BitMart is also hosting a Vote for Your Coin â€“ Round 2 Campaign to let users vote for their favorite coins to be listed on BitMart Exchange. The winner will be listed without a listing fee. Participants can also vote for free, unlike most campaigns by other exchanges, and have a chance to win free tokens for promoting the coin of their choice on social media.  BitMartâ€™s short-term goal is to propel BitMart into the top 10 for global cryptocurrency exchanges and to reach a global website traffic ranking within the top 50,000. BitMartâ€™s long-term goal is to become a whole-network trading platform providing one-stop financial solutions for cryptocurrency trading, as well as small business enterprises.  When asked about the future vision for BitMart, Founder & CEO Sheldon Xia, stated recently, â€œI hope BitMart will become a fast and reliable exchange for users trading digital assets, as well as one that brings more innovation to the industry.â€

Author: BitMartExchange
Title: ã€Announcementã€‘BitMart Trading Platform is Comingï¼
Body: https://i.imgur.com/7hFIv7x.jpg https://i.imgur.com/BknOwwR.jpg https://i.imgur.com/9GiDftZ.jpg https://i.imgur.com/BaGwSN3.jpg https://i.imgur.com/WQaSivs.jpg https://i.imgur.com/fvWyIU3.jpg https://i.imgur.com/SF4pcq2.png   BiMart Exchange  As a globally integrated trading platform, BitMart provides reliable cryptocurrency services such as spot trading, futures contract trading, over-the-counter trading, and whole-network trading. Meanwhile, BitMart will provide the technical, financial, and marketing solutions for conventional business. In addition, BitMart is developing an incubator to build the bridge between traditional business and digital asset world.  It is believed that BitMart would bring more innovation, efficiency, and equality to the world with the ambition to be the NASDAQ in the digital asset market.  Pre-ICO and ICO  "BMX" is the token of BitMart. BitMart issued 100,000,000 BMX tokens during the Pre-ICO campaign running from December 18, 2017 (UTC) to December 25, 2018 (UTC). The token public sale ran from December 28, 2017 (UTC) to January 15, 2018 (UTC). Due to an ETH bull run, BitMart achieved sufficient financial support in the whitelist phase, so then in the public sale phase, BitMart decided to reduce the token amount from 300 million to 100 million and destroy the remaining 200 million (token price remains at 1ETH = 10000BMX). Due to over-subscription during the whitelist stage, the total ETH collected reached 10,052.7, with 962.7 ETH overfilled compared to 9,090 ETH planned (10.59% overfill). Based on pre-established subscription rules, BitMart returned the overfilled ETH to each user's account. However, as this could cause profit loss to some of the early participants, BitMart gave away 10.59% BMX to all subscribers who had successfully participated in the whitelist phase (in total 110,590,000 BMX). This part of BMX will be extracted from the to-be-destroyed 200 million BMX.  Public sale announcement: https://support.bitmart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000018554-BMX-Public-Sale-Announcement, Token destroy announcement: https://support.bitmart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000116393-BMX-Destroyed-Announcement.  Beta Test Announcement  We are so excited to announce that BitMart Beta Test opening now. It is our honor to inform you that you have the privilege to experience the brand new features of BitMart Exchange. We sincerely hope that you can share your comments and suggestions with us.  Beta Test Website: https://b.bitmart.com/  Contact us Telegram: https://t.me/BitMartExchange Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/BitMartExchange/ https://support.bitmart.com/hc/en-us/requests/new support@bitmart.com.  Notice*: Beta Test Account is not linked to your www.BitMart.com account, you need to register a new one. (If you join our Alpha Test, you can use that account). Also, upload a screenshot of your Beta Test page to google form: https://goo.gl/ne6WUG,  we will send FREE 15 BMX to your www.BitMart.com account.  BitMart Exchange  Our official website (www.bitmart.com) has launched. You can log in, register and deposit. The trading feature will be online on March 15th, 2018. More detailed here: https://support.bitmart.com/hc/en-us/articles/360001484773-Open-Registration-and-Deposit-Announcement  More Information   Website: www.bitmart.com Whitepaper: https://www.bitmart.com/whitepaper/bitmart_whitepaper_en.pdf Twitter:  twitter.com/BitMartExchange   Facebookï¼šfacebook.com/BitMartExchange Reddit:  reddit.com/user/bitmartexchange Telegramï¼šhttps://t.me/BitMartexchange
